<title type="html"><![CDATA[11/14(Thu.) Gays issue/ Depression(host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=334&amp;p=350#p350"><![CDATA[
Gays issue<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/lang/archives/2019/10/25/2003724573">http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/lang/ar ... 2003724573</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taiwan_Pride">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taiwan_Pride</a><!-- m --><br /> <br />1.         Why do you think a person becomes a gay or lesbian?<br />2.         Do you accept a homosexual? Why or why not?<br />3.         What do you think our law about this issue?<br />4.         Do you support their parade weeks ago in Taipei ?<br />5.         Do you have any story to share about gays?<br />Depression<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/k-pop-singer-found-dead-in-suspected-suicide-highlighting-mental-health-pressures/2019/10/14/1e69a8de-ee67-11e9-bb7e-d2026ee0c199_story.html">https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/as ... story.html</a><!-- m --><br />1.         Why do you think a person get depressed? Genetic, environmental, personality problem? <br />2.         Did you ever feel depressed? Why?<br />3.         Do you think there is a cure for depression?<br />4.         Did you ever hear any story about people suffering from serious depression? How did you help them out?<br />Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. Free talk<br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. First topic discussion<br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. Second topic discussion<br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation (Participants that haven't presented yet are invited)<br /><br />speaker time: 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time: 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Sun Nov 10, 2019 9:40 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
